/h5><p>包含空闲和总系统时间的对象。Object containing idle and total CPU time</p>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Get raw CPU timing data</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">cpuInfo</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">getCPUInfo</span>();\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">usagePercent</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> ((<span class=\"pl-smi\">cpuInfo</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">total</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">-</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">cpuInfo</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">idle</span>) <span class=\"pl-k\">/</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">cpuInfo</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">total</span>) <span class=\"pl-k\">*</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">100</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span>Instantaneous CPU usage: ${<span class=\"pl-smi\">usagePercent</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">toFixed</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span>)}%<span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Calculate CPU usage over time</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">start</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">getCPUInfo</span>();\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">setTimeout</span>(() <span class=\"pl-k\">=></span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">end</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">getCPUInfo</span>();\n  <span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">idleDiff</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">end</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">idle</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">-</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">start</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">idle</span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">totalDiff</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">end</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">total</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">-</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">start</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">total</span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">usage</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">-</span> (<span class=\"pl-smi\">idleDiff</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">/</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">totalDiff</span>);\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span>CPU usage over 1 second: ${(<span class=\"pl-smi\">usage</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">*</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">100</span>).<span class=\"pl-en\">toFixed</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span>)}%<span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span></span>);\n}, <span class=\"pl-c1\">1000</span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Since:</h5><p>1.0.0</p>\n<h5>See:</h5><ul>\n<li><a href=\"2211\">getCPUUsage</a> - Higher-level CPU usage monitoring</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/os.html#os_os_cpus\">https://nodejs.org/api/os.html#os_os_cpus</a> - Node.js os.cpus() documentation</li>\n</ul>\n"},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/node-utils/src/system/os.ts","fullFileName":"/home/runner/work/fe-tools/fe-tools/utils/packages/node-utils/src/system/os.ts","line":708,"character":0,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3274750/utils/packages/node-utils/src/system/os.ts#L708"}],"parentId":2221}],"is":{"declaration":true},"location":{"query":"node-utils/src.Function.getCPUInfo","hash":""},"text":{},"parentId":965}
